    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "spawner_class_fields",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 330,
      "text": "  trigger(prompt, trigger_source, context, max_turns,\n           parent_context, request_id, complexity)\n     → SpawnerResult\n\n  _run(...)  [called under semaphore]\n\n  stop_accepting()   drain(timeout=30.0)\n\n  ── State ──\n  _session_semaphore: asyncio.Semaphore(max_concurrent)\n  _max_queued_sessions: int\n  _accepting: bool\n  _in_flight: set[asyncio.Task]\n  _adapter_pool: dict[str, RuntimeAdapter]\n  _metrics: ButlerMetrics\n\n  ── Concurrency guards ──\n  trigger-source deadlock: reject if _value == 0\n  queue-full rejection: if waiters >= max_queued",
      "originalText": "  trigger(prompt, trigger_source, context, max_turns,\n           parent_context, request_id, complexity)\n     → SpawnerResult\n\n  _run(...)  [called under semaphore]\n\n  stop_accepting()   drain(timeout=30.0)\n\n  ── State ──\n  _session_semaphore: asyncio.Semaphore(max_concurrent)\n  _max_queued_sessions: int\n  _accepting: bool\n  _in_flight: set[asyncio.Task]\n  _adapter_pool: dict[str, RuntimeAdapter]\n  _metrics: ButlerMetrics\n\n  ── Concurrency guards ──\n  trigger-source deadlock: reject if _value == 0\n  queue-full rejection: if waiters >= max_queued",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a8a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
