    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "hot_path_text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 2318,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "ingest → enqueue(ref, tier) → tier_queue.put(ref)\n  → worker → pipeline.process()\n\nBackpressure: when all tier queues full,\n  hot path skips enqueue (message stays in\n  message_inbox with lifecycle_state='accepted')\n  → scanner recovers on next sweep",
      "originalText": "ingest → enqueue(ref, tier) → tier_queue.put(ref)\n  → worker → pipeline.process()\n\nBackpressure: when all tier queues full,\n  hot path skips enqueue (message stays in\n  message_inbox with lifecycle_state='accepted')\n  → scanner recovers on next sweep",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#7f1d1d",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
