    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "error_handling_text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 3028,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 210,
      "text": "except Exception as exc:\n  discard_runtime_session_tool_calls(session_id)\n  duration_ms = elapsed\n  span.set_status(ERROR, str(exc))\n  span.record_exception(exc)\n  → SpawnerResult(success=False, error=msg)\n  session_complete(pool, session_id,\n                   success=False, error=msg)\n  session_process_log_write() [best-effort]\n\nConcurrency rejection paths (→ SpawnerResult.success=False):\n  • trigger-source deadlock: semaphore._value == 0\n  • queue full: waiters >= max_queued_sessions\n  • spawner stopped: _accepting = False\n    → RuntimeError('Spawner shutting down')\n\nAdapter reset: runtime.reset() on failed invocation\n  (adapters with cached provider clients clear stale state)",
      "originalText": "except Exception as exc:\n  discard_runtime_session_tool_calls(session_id)\n  duration_ms = elapsed\n  span.set_status(ERROR, str(exc))\n  span.record_exception(exc)\n  → SpawnerResult(success=False, error=msg)\n  session_complete(pool, session_id,\n                   success=False, error=msg)\n  session_process_log_write() [best-effort]\n\nConcurrency rejection paths (→ SpawnerResult.success=False):\n  • trigger-source deadlock: semaphore._value == 0\n  • queue full: waiters >= max_queued_sessions\n  • spawner stopped: _accepting = False\n    → RuntimeError('Spawner shutting down')\n\nAdapter reset: runtime.reset() on failed invocation\n  (adapters with cached provider clients clear stale state)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#881337",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 107014,
      "version": 1,
